{"sn2.19:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 2.19 ","sn2.19:0.2":"2. Anathapindikavagga ","sn2.19:0.3":"Uttarasutta ","sn2.19:1.1":"Rajagahanidanam. ","sn2.19:1.2":"Ekamantam thito kho uttaro devaputto bhagavato santike imam gatham abhasi: ","sn2.19:2.1":"“Upaniyati jivitamappamayu, ","sn2.19:2.2":"Jarupanitassa na santi tana; ","sn2.19:2.3":"Etam bhayam marane pekkhamano, ","sn2.19:2.4":"Punnani kayiratha sukhavahani”ti. ","sn2.19:3.1":"“Upaniyati jivitamappamayu, ","sn2.19:3.2":"Jarupanitassa na santi tana; ","sn2.19:3.3":"Etam bhayam marane pekkhamano, ","sn2.19:3.4":"Lokamisam pajahe santipekkho”ti. "}